cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.DM

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with languages and their subword relation. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper extends first-order logic with new quantifiers. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper discusses decidability of theories. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with regular predicates and subword relations, which are topics in discrete mathematics.
